{"tid":1538923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林奠唔通真係港獨之母","createTime":"2019-09-04T08:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T08:27:19.000Z","uid":8647,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"627d6f0f31f2380d76bac66a8d50e18b203efe4e","tid":1538923,"uid":8647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:18:28.000Z","msg":"1/9 塞機場雖然有成效，但都未迫到正苦讓步，而果次大搜捕應該嚇窒唔少人，令到啲人未必下次塞機場會再出黎。<br />\n<br />\n但衣家呢個時候又傳將會正式撒回條例，話你知正苦頂唔撚住要讓步<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每次林奠出黎都比啲動力令你下次再上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係開始信林奠係港獨之母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e23b3371093108553d09f83f7337f92bf459d0c","tid":1538923,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:19:05.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ef016d268edeb2c4bfa06b76abfabb58eea957","tid":1538923,"uid":197121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:21:02.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n即刻9月8號出美領揸春袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1853fcd74eaa27bb50e8b1b459e0c30247a9dd","tid":1538923,"uid":2479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:21:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n9月8 要人</span><br />\n<br />\n全世界9月8號出俾佢睇！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538569\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538569</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b7700d085be085fed78b6e4298174b3cbd28954b","tid":1538923,"uid":8647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2b5bc0166999f88ae75a61041b2f0b29e796517","tid":1538923,"uid":8647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:27:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}